              %h2 Logo:
              %p The logo of Manthan International School depicts a couple of birds flying around the glowing sun. The suggestion, without any doubt, is birds learn to fly, soar high and utilize the light of the sun to acquire a distinctive panoramic view of things, a unique perspective. Manthan desires that all its students learn how to learn and use their abilities to learn creatively to bring in “a light that never was on land and sea” and thereby add special worth to things.

