              %h2 School Description:
              %p Manthan Madhapur runs classes from Jr KG to Class 8. Manthan Gachiblowli - a second campus is planned with in 5 minute drive from Gachibowli Wipro junction over 5 acres in Tellapur Village that will eventually have classes from Jr KG to Class 12. Gachibowli campus will be operational in June 2014 for classess Jr Kg to Class 9.Admissions for the Madhapur School are in progress for classes Jr KG to Class 3. Admissions for Tellapur Campus are in progress for classes Jr KG to Class 9 for the academic year starting June 2014.
              %p Manthan is promoted and run by a group of professionals with a passion for education. It is set up with a mission to build socially aware and responsible citizens. 
